Package: pkginstall
Title: Installs Packages from Local Files
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R:
    c(person("Jim", "Hester", email = "james.f.hester@gmail.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Gábor", "Gábor", email = "csardi.gabor@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides a replacement for `utils::install.packages(repo = NULL)`.
    I.e. it builds binary packages from source packages, and extracts the
    compressed archives into the package library.
License: GPL-3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1)
